---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-16 border-t border-base-border bg-base-surface">
  <div class="container-content py-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-ink-secondary sm:flex-row">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-accent">▶</span>
        <span class="font-semibold text-ink-primary">Hexen</span>
        <span>· TMDB + Moviebox</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center sm:text-right">
        All videos and pictures are from the Internet; copyrights belong to their original creators.
        <br />Hexen only provides a webpage service and does not store, record, or upload any content.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-xs text-ink-secondary">© {year} Hexen · Built with Astro + Svelte</p>
  </div>
</footer>
